trans-unit.source: Releases all resources used by the <xref href="System.IdentityModel.Claims.WindowsClaimSet"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Libera todos os recursos usados pelo <xref href="System.IdentityModel.Claims.WindowsClaimSet"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Call the Dispose method when you are finished using the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Claims.WindowsClaimSet>.
trans-unit.target: Chamar o método Dispose quando terminar de usar o <xref:System.IdentityModel.Claims.WindowsClaimSet>.</xref:System.IdentityModel.Claims.WindowsClaimSet>

trans-unit.source: The Dispose method leaves the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Claims.WindowsClaimSet> in an unusable state.
trans-unit.target: O método Dispose deixa a <xref:System.IdentityModel.Claims.WindowsClaimSet>em um estado inutilizável.</xref:System.IdentityModel.Claims.WindowsClaimSet>

trans-unit.source: After calling the Dispose method, you must release all references to the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Claims.WindowsClaimSet> so that the garbage collector can reclaim the memory that the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Claims.WindowsClaimSet> occupied.
trans-unit.target: Depois de chamar o método Dispose, você deve liberar todas as referências para o <xref:System.IdentityModel.Claims.WindowsClaimSet>para que o coletor de lixo possa recuperar a memória que o <xref:System.IdentityModel.Claims.WindowsClaimSet>ocupado.</xref:System.IdentityModel.Claims.WindowsClaimSet> </xref:System.IdentityModel.Claims.WindowsClaimSet>

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Cleaning Up Unmanaged Resources](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) and [Implementing a Dispose Method](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Para obter mais informações, consulte [limpeza de recursos não gerenciados](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) e [implementar um método Dispose](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Always call the Dispose method before you release your last reference to the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Claims.WindowsClaimSet>.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Sempre chamar o método Dispose antes de liberar sua última referência a <xref:System.IdentityModel.Claims.WindowsClaimSet>.</xref:System.IdentityModel.Claims.WindowsClaimSet>

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, the resources it is using are not freed until the garbage collector calls the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Claims.WindowsClaimSet> object's `Finalize` method.
trans-unit.target: Caso contrário, os recursos que está usando não são liberados até o coletor de lixo chama o <xref:System.IdentityModel.Claims.WindowsClaimSet>do objeto `Finalize` método.</xref:System.IdentityModel.Claims.WindowsClaimSet>
